## Splitting epics (`T-0xx`) — Product Map Delivery layer

Перед разбиением: **MVP slice** (In/Out) и **North Star / OMTM** в brief (фаза 3). Каждый `T-0xx` = deliverable из карты (requirement → story → AC).

| Rule | Example |
|------|---------|
| One **shippable slice** per task (≤ ~1–2 dev days) | T-010 «Guest detail read» separate from «Booking create» if large |
| **Vertical** slice preferred (UI + API + seed) | `/finance` entry for one `RevenueLine` type |
| **Horizontal** only for shared infra | T-002 schema before module UIs |
| Number **sequentially**; never reuse IDs | Next free after highest in queue |
| Epic name in «Детали» Notes + **фаза карты** | Epic «Phase 3 CRM» → T-010… (Delivery) |
| Приоритет | P0/P1 rubric + impact на метрики пилота (Analysis) |

