## Anti-patterns (avoid)

- Task without AC or with «сделать красиво»
- Same ID `IN_PROGRESS` in two chats/agents
- `READY` while dependency task not `DONE` (unless Architect waived)
- PM editing `app/`, `modules/`, `prisma/` without explicit Human request
- 10 tasks `IN_PROGRESS`; max **one per role per agent**
- Closing epic by marking one subtask `DONE` and ignoring siblings

