## Product Map 3.10 — discovery checklist & templates

**Cheatsheet (RU):** `@knowledge-base/product-map-3.10-cheatsheet.md`  
**Session log:** `@knowledge-base/product-map-workflow.md`

**External (Human; PM does not log in to SaaS):** [productmap.io](https://www.productmap.io/) · [PM Map 3.10](https://www.productmap.io/product-management-map) · [TASK](https://www.productmap.io/task-agentic-product-management) · [Figma 3.10](https://www.figma.com/board/SABujfIEwzpa1NuWiVS3RR/The-Product-Map-3.10?node-id=100-6433) · [create project](https://app.productmap.io/profile/assistant/create-project) (optional)

**PDF / Figma:** automated PDF text often empty (visual map). Ask Human for frame export or branch titles; until then use cheatsheet + website taxonomy.

### When Human shares links (same as every grooming session)

1. Map input to **phase 1–4 + People**; update artifacts table (§ Management & roadmap).
2. Run checklist below; gaps → `BLOCKED`.
3. Log session in `product-map-workflow.md` + «Журнал».

### Discovery checklist (Strategy → People)

**Strategy**

- [ ] One-sentence **vision** (12 months)?
- [ ] **ICP** / primary segment (who pays, who uses)?
- [ ] **Business model** hook (revenue, unit economics focus)?
- [ ] Top **3 goals** this quarter?

**Generation (users & problems)**

- [ ] **Personas** (2–4): role, goal, pain, success signal?
- [ ] **JTBD** per persona: «When … I want … so I can …»?
- [ ] **Problem statement** (see template): who, pain, impact, current workaround?
- [ ] **Alternatives** / competitors / spreadsheets today?

**Analysis**

- [ ] **North Star** or pilot **OMTM**?
- [ ] **Success metrics** (baseline → target → timeframe)?
- [ ] **Risks** (top 5: prob × impact)?

**Delivery**

- [ ] **MVP slice** for next phase (in / out)?
- [ ] **Dependencies** (auth, legal, data, integrations)?
- [ ] Ready to break into **vertical** `T-0xx`?

**People**

- [ ] **Stakeholders** and decision owner?
- [ ] **Pilot** participants and cadence?

### Cursor workflow ≈ app «Create project» (mandatory for new / Phase N)

| Step | Product Map app | Muster PM |
|------|-----------------|-----------|
| 1 | Product context | `product-map-workflow.md` + brief header |
| 2 | Copilot mode | greenfield / daily PM / pilot — note in workflow |
| 3 | Organize context | `@` links in every `T-0xx` row |
| 4 | Skills gaps | PM/Architect `BLOCKED`; execution → other agents |
| 5 | Assistant tasks | Checklist → brief/roadmap → `T-0xx` + Product Map gate |
| 6 | Save knowledge | Queue + workflow always; git commit when Human asks |

### Templates (copy into brief or workflow log)

**Problem statement**

```markdown
**Для** [persona/ICP]
**который** [situation + pain]
**продукт** [name] — [key capability]
**в отличие от** [alternative]
**мы** [measurable outcome]
```

**Persona (one row)**

```markdown
| Имя/роль | Цель | Боль | Триггер успеха | Модули |
```

**JTBD**

```markdown
Когда [situation], я хочу [motivation], чтобы [outcome].
```

**Success metrics**

```markdown
| Метрика | Baseline | Target | Срок | Источник данных |
```

**MVP slice (next phase)**

```markdown
**In:** …
**Out:** …
**Pilot success:** …
**Stop criteria:** …
```

**Risks**

```markdown
| Риск | P | I | Mitigation | Owner |
```

